  "description": "Your personal internet supercomputer — fast, free and private. A content-addressed operating system for the open, semantic web: every object is a self-verifying W3C linked-data node named by its content (did:holo:sha256:…), composing into one infinitely-nestable, serverless object graph. Resolve any reference, re-derive its hash, and you have verified it — no server to trust.",
